  "alternative_titles": "I Got Possessed Into a Manga I've Never Read, I Possessed a Character in a Manga I Don't Know, I Was Possessed by an Unknown Manga, I Was Reincarnated Into an Unknown Manga, I Was Thrown Into an Unfamiliar Manga, Tôi Bị Ném Vào Thế Giới Manga Xa Lạ, Xuyên Vào Bộ Manga Vô Danh, 成为漫画学院的配角, 目立ちたくない俺のモブキャラ人生, 모르는 만화에 빙의했다",
